headline.main: Hit Man in San Antonio Murder-For-Hire Slaying Set to Die
headline.print_headline: Hit Man in San Antonio Murder-For-Hire Slaying Set to Die

lead_paragraph: A contract killer on death row for fatally shooting a woman outside her San Antonio home nearly a quarter-century ago is set to die this week in Texas.
